local function toggleHB() hitboxEnabled=not hitboxEnabled playSound(hitboxEnabled and "on" or "off") notify("Luna",hitboxEnabled and "Hitbox ON" or "Hitbox OFF",2) if HBStatus then HBStatus.Text=hitboxEnabled and T("hb_on") or T("hb_off") HBStatus.TextColor3=hitboxEnabled and GREEN or RED_COL end saveState() end
local function toggleCS() carSpeedEnabled=not carSpeedEnabled if carSpeedEnabled then playSound("on") notify("Luna","CarSpeed ON",2) if CSStatus then CSStatus.Text=T("cs_on") CSStatus.TextColor3=GREEN end else carSpeedDir=0 playSound("off") notify("Luna","CarSpeed OFF",2) if CSStatus then CSStatus.Text=T("cs_off") CSStatus.TextColor3=RED_COL end end saveState() end
local function toggleESP()
  builtinESPOn=not builtinESPOn
  if not builtinESPOn then
    for _,h in pairs(espHighlights) do pcall(function() if h and h.Parent then h:Destroy() end end) end
    for _,b in pairs(espBillboards) do pcall(function() if b and b.Parent then b:Destroy() end end) end
    espHighlights={} espBillboards={}
  end
  playSound(builtinESPOn and "on" or "off")
  notify("ESP",builtinESPOn and "ESP ON" or "ESP OFF",2)
  if BespStatus then BespStatus.Text=builtinESPOn and T("besp_on") or T("besp_off") BespStatus.TextColor3=builtinESPOn and GREEN or RED_COL end
end
local function toggleStretch()
  if currentAspect~=nil then
    currentAspect=nil applyAspectRatio(nil)
    notify("Luna","Stretch: OFF",2) playSound("off")
  else
    local defaultRatio=4/3
    currentAspect=defaultRatio applyAspectRatio(defaultRatio)
    notify("Luna","Stretch: 4:3",2) playSound("on")
  end
end

local function matchBind(b,inp) if not b then return false end if b.kind=="Key" then return inp.KeyCode and inp.KeyCode==b.code elseif b.kind=="Mouse" then local ut=inp.UserInputType if b.btn==4 then return ut==Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton4 end if b.btn==5 then return ut==Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton5 end if b.btn==3 then return ut==Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton3 end end return false end
local function inpStr(inp) if inp.KeyCode and inp.KeyCode~=Enum.KeyCode.Unknown then return tostring(inp.KeyCode):gsub("Enum.KeyCode.","") end local ut=inp.UserInputType if ut==Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton3 then return "Mouse3" end if ut==Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton4 then return "Mouse4" end if ut==Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton5 then return "Mouse5" end return "?" end

UIS.InputBegan:Connect(function(inp,gp)
  if listeningFor then
    if inp.KeyCode==Enum.KeyCode.Delete then
      local key=listeningFor listeningFor=nil binds[key]=nil
      if bindLabels[key] then bindLabels[key].Text="---" bindLabels[key].TextColor3=SUBTEXT end return end
    local str=inpStr(inp) if str=="?" then return end local key=listeningFor listeningFor=nil
    if inp.KeyCode and inp.KeyCode~=Enum.KeyCode.Unknown then binds[key]={kind="Key",code=inp.KeyCode}
    else local ut=inp.UserInputType local n=0 if ut==Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton3 then n=3 elseif ut==Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton4 then n=4 elseif ut==Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton5 then n=5 end if n>0 then binds[key]={kind="Mouse",btn=n} end end
    if bindLabels[key] then bindLabels[key].Text=bStr(binds[key]) bindLabels[key].TextColor3=ACCENT end return end
  if gp then return end
  if inp.KeyCode==Enum.KeyCode.Quote and _switchFlyMode then _switchFlyMode() return end
  if matchBind(binds.fly,inp) and _toggleFly then _toggleFly() end
  if matchBind(binds.hb,inp) then toggleHB() end
  if matchBind(binds.cs,inp) then toggleCS() end
  if matchBind(binds.esp,inp) then toggleESP() end
  if matchBind(binds.stretch,inp) then toggleStretch() end
  if matchBind(binds.menu,inp) then opened=not opened if opened then openUI() else closeUI() end end end)
UIS.InputBegan:Connect(function(k,gp) if gp then return end local d=getDir(k) if d then carSpeedDir=d end end)
UIS.InputEnded:Connect(function(k,gp) if gp then return end if getDir(k)==carSpeedDir then carSpeedDir=0 end end)

